CORE OBJECTIVE
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

Create a single ultra-realistic fashion advertising image where an oversized version of the referenced product is the main hero prop, supported by a playful, fashion-forward talent pose.

This is:
- commercial advertising
- fashion editorial in tone
- playful and energetic
- clean and modern

It is NOT abstract.
It is NOT surreal.
It is NOT illustrative.

